txt.en: 'Hail, [placeholder]! You assisted in defeating Núrzum, but the enemy has not given up. They still roam our lands and lurk in the shadows.\n\n'The High Knolls Blizzard, a deadly cluster of frost grims, has settled into the hills of the High Knolls. Go there, and show them that Wildermore will endure!'
You have defeated the High Knolls Blizzard, earning the gratitude of the people of Wildermore.
Warband II: The High Knolls Blizzard
<rgb=#FF0000>Completing Wildermore's Recovery will cancel this quest.</rgb>
Núrzum has been defeated, but the enemy persists throughout much of Wildermore. The High Knolls Blizzard, a deadly cluster of frost grims, has settled into the hills of the High Knolls.
The High Knolls Blizzard can be found moving up and down the High Knolls area of Wildermore.
You have defeated the High Knolls Blizzard, earning the gratitude of the people of Wildermore.
